# TailAdmin Design Memory (EMS)

## Policy (exact)

- **In code:** Employee Management System only. **No TailAdmin demo pages** in `src/` or routes.
- **In memory (this rule):** Remember **all** TailAdmin design patterns below.
- **When a related EMS component/feature is added:** follow the matching TailAdmin design from this rule (and the external template if detail is needed). Do not invent a new look.

This app is an **Employee Management System**. UI must follow **TailAdmin** design. Demo pages/data must **not** live in the codebase.

**External template (look up details when implementing a pattern):**  
`D:/templates/tailadmin-free-tailwind-dashboard-template-main`

**Live EMS embodiments:** `AppShell`, `Sidebar`, `Header`, `DashboardPage`, list pages, `PageCard`, `Breadcrumb`, `ModalShell`, auth pages, `formLayoutModel.js`, form field components.

## Hard rules

1. **Do not** re-add TailAdmin demo routes/pages (Alerts, Badges, Buttons, Avatars, Form Elements demo, Basic Tables demo, Charts demo, Calendar demo, Blank promo, Map, eCommerce orders, UI Elements menu, TailAdmin promo).
2. **Do** implement the matching TailAdmin **layout/components** when an EMS feature needs that UI (e.g. leave approve → ModalShell; create employee → form grid + PageCard; payroll alerts → alert banner classes).
3. **Always** MVC: client `views → controllers → services → API` (models for validation/constants); server `routes → controllers → models`.
4. Prefer existing components over new one-off styles.

---

## 1. App shell

- Root: `flex h-screen overflow-hidden`
- Content: `mx-auto max-w-(--breakpoint-2xl) p-4 md:p-6`
- Sidebar: ~290px / collapsed 90px, `border-r`, active item `bg-brand-50 text-brand-500`
- Header: sticky, search `h-11 shadow-theme-xs`, dropdowns `rounded-2xl shadow-theme-lg`
- Reference: `AppShell.jsx`, `Sidebar.jsx`, `Header.jsx`, `utils/tw.js`

## 2. Dashboard (12-column)

```
grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 md:gap-6
  xl:col-span-7 → primary metric pair + bar chart
  xl:col-span-5 → radial target card
  col-span-12   → secondary KPI strip / area statistics chart
  xl:col-span-5 → list with progress bars (demographics-style)
  xl:col-span-7 → recent table (Filter / See all buttons)
```

- Metric card: `rounded-2xl border p-5 md:p-6`, icon `h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-gray-100`, trend pill success/error
- Chart shells: `rounded-2xl border …` + `ChartActionsMenu`
- Radial card: gray outer wrap, white inner, badge, message, footer stats with `h-7 w-px` dividers
- Area chart: tab pill group `bg-gray-100 p-0.5`, active tab `bg-white shadow-theme-xs`
- Reference: `DashboardPage.jsx`, `MetricCards`, `ChartOne/Two/Three`, `DepartmentOverview`, `RecentActivitiesTable`

## 3. Page chrome

- `Breadcrumb`: H2 + Home › pageName
- `PageCard`: `rounded-2xl border`, header `px-6 py-5`, optional subtitle, body `border-t`
- Empty module shell (when content not ready yet): `Breadcrumb` + `min-h-[…] rounded-2xl border bg-white px-5 py-7` (no TailAdmin marketing copy)

## 4. Tables

- Outer: `overflow-hidden rounded-xl border …` + `overflow-x-auto`
- Head: `text-theme-xs font-medium text-gray-500`
- Body: `divide-y`; primary `text-theme-sm font-medium text-gray-800`; muted `text-gray-500`
- Status pill: `inline-flex rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-theme-xs font-medium`
  - success: `bg-success-50 text-success-700 dark:bg-success-500/15 dark:text-success-500`
  - error: `bg-error-50 text-error-700 …`
  - warning: `bg-warning-50 text-warning-700 …`
  - info: `bg-blue-light-50 text-blue-light-700 …`
- Row avatar: `h-10 w-10 rounded-full`
- Reference: Employees / Departments / Attendance / Leave Requests pages

## 5. Forms

Token file: `src/models/formLayoutModel.js`  
Fields: `PasswordField`, `SelectField`

When building EMS create/edit forms:

- `Breadcrumb` + one or more `PageCard` sections
- `FORM_STACK_CLASS` / `FORM_GRID_CLASS` (`sm:grid-cols-2`)
- Labels: `LABEL_CLASS` + required `text-error-500` asterisk
- Controls: `INPUT_CLASS`, `SELECT_CLASS`, `TEXTAREA_CLASS`
- Primary submit: `rounded-lg bg-brand-500 text-white hover:bg-brand-600 shadow-theme-xs`
- Secondary: `border border-gray-300 bg-white … shadow-theme-xs`
- State in controllers; no fetch in views

## 6. Auth

- `AuthLayout`: split form | brand panel `bg-brand-950` + `CommonGridShape`
- Keep brand text EMS-specific (not TailAdmin marketing)
- Reference: `SignInPage`, `SignUpPage`

## 7. Modals

- `ModalShell`: backdrop blur, panel `max-w-[700px] rounded-3xl`, close circle button
- Form fields inside use form tokens / 2-col grid as in Profile modals
- Footer: brand primary + outline cancel

## 8. Alerts / badges / buttons / avatars (apply when EMS needs them)

Do **not** ship demo galleries. When the feature needs the UI, use:

- **Alert banners:** `rounded-xl border border-{tone}-500 bg-{tone}-50 p-4` (+ dark `/15` variants) for success / error / warning / info
- **Soft badges:** `rounded-full bg-brand-50 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-sm text-brand-500` (and success/error/warning/info equivalents)
- **Primary button:** `rounded-lg bg-brand-500 … hover:bg-brand-600`
- **Outline button:** `rounded-lg border border-gray-300 bg-white … shadow-theme-xs`
- **Avatars:** `rounded-full` sized `h-6`–`h-16` as context requires

Pull visual detail from the HTML template under `D:/templates/tailadmin-free-...` if needed, then implement once for EMS data.

## 9. Charts pages

If a dedicated chart view is needed later: wrap Apex chart in `PageCard` / bordered card, reuse `chartModel` option shapes, EMS series from API — no sample “Sales/Revenue” demo routes.

## 10. Design tokens (`index.css`)

- Brand: `#465fff` (`brand-500`)
- Font: Outfit
- Type: `text-theme-xs/sm`, `text-title-sm`
- Shadows: `shadow-theme-xs/sm/md/lg`
- Cards: `rounded-2xl border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-white/[0.03]`
- App is **light theme only** — do not add a dark-mode toggle or theme controller.

